channel.title: When i try to list
channel.description:
I get this error when i try to list my server, it isnt offline as you can see..
[IMG]http://i785.photobucket.com/albums/yy140/Kanichiwa1/-_-.png[/img]
any ideas on what im doing wrong?
I AM using no-ip correctly..

item.title: When i try to list
item.dc:creator: @Brandontan Brandontan
item.description:
@Brandontan wrote:

1, make sure you are port forwarded
2, go to canyouseeme.org and type in the port (43594) in your case
3, if its good, make sure the downloadable client is good (working)
4, if all others work, read the message it says at the top of the site…
THIS NEW PAGE IS BETA

Hope this helps, but InsidiaX is not a good source for beginners, if you are one.
good luck
